title: Adamivka, Zhytomyr Oblast
content:
Adamivka (Ukrainian: Адамівка Adamivka) is a village in northern Ukraine, in Zviahel Raion of Zhytomyr Oblast. The code KOATUUI: 1820655401. Its population is 15 people as 2001. Its postal index is 12724. Its calling code is 4144.

The village council is located at 12734, Ukraine, Zhytomyr Oblast, Baranivskiy district, town Dovbysh (urban-type settlement), st. Shchosa, 20.
